data.description: Lovely 2 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom townhome in Stuart! This perfect starter unit or investment opportunity is located in the wonderful community of River Pine and offers a spacious layout in a very convenient location. Upon entering this unit you will find a spacious living room area leading to the kitchen with plenty of windows allowing for natural light and beautiful neutral paint throughout. In the kitchen you will find lots of wooden cabinets for storage space. The exterior of this home features a large balcony overlooking the front patio area. This home is conveniently located just minutes from major roadways, shopping, dining and more!
